WEBVTT

01:38.080 --> 01:40.710
[Fate Chooses You]

01:41.410 --> 01:43.560
[Episode 8]

01:45.229 --> 01:46.200
What are you doing?

01:46.200 --> 01:48.259
Honestly, watch where you're going.

01:54.310 --> 01:56.039
Don't drink the water.

01:56.400 --> 01:57.660
Don't drink the water.

01:57.759 --> 01:58.620
It's poisoned!

01:59.280 --> 02:00.280
Don't drink the water.

02:00.280 --> 02:02.230
It's poisoned!

02:02.430 --> 02:04.400
It's poisoned!

02:04.560 --> 02:05.920
Don't drink the water!

02:06.070 --> 02:07.040
It's poisoned!

02:08.419 --> 02:09.080
Why did he fall?

02:09.080 --> 02:10.150
Is it really poisoned?

02:10.150 --> 02:11.590
You should stay away from
a person like him.

02:11.590 --> 02:12.590
Look, he fainted.

02:17.680 --> 02:19.610
That guy was acting crazy just now.

02:19.710 --> 02:21.360
There must be something wrong
with his mind.

02:21.360 --> 02:22.290
Did he scare you?

02:22.400 --> 02:22.910
No.

02:23.280 --> 02:23.910
Thank you.

02:25.190 --> 02:27.190
Stay away from
this kind of person in the future.

02:27.190 --> 02:28.490
And don't ever be like last time—

02:28.490 --> 02:29.430
walking into any shady roadside inn

02:29.430 --> 02:30.310
in the middle of nowhere,

02:30.310 --> 02:32.510
drinking whatever strangers hand you.

02:38.000 --> 02:39.660
You really don't remember me?

02:41.680 --> 02:42.680
What a bad memory!

02:45.120 --> 02:45.630
Wait,

02:45.800 --> 02:47.060
what's wrong with you?

02:47.190 --> 02:47.920
Are you okay?

03:10.960 --> 03:13.000
Looks like someone is resting inside.

03:13.000 --> 03:13.680
Let's go in.

03:16.430 --> 03:17.230
What's wrong?

03:17.360 --> 03:17.890
Let's go.

03:18.079 --> 03:18.520
No.

03:18.960 --> 03:20.160
Do you really know me?

03:22.800 --> 03:24.710
I am a bounty guard of
Dongzhou Prefecture.

03:24.710 --> 03:26.190
I am here on official business.

03:26.190 --> 03:27.590
We just happened to meet.

03:28.430 --> 03:29.910
You are just a minor cultivator,

03:29.910 --> 03:31.370
but you are quite on guard.

03:31.520 --> 03:32.980
You know I'm a cultivator?

03:37.680 --> 03:38.740
It's going to rain.

03:38.750 --> 03:39.680
Let's go inside.

03:42.840 --> 03:43.310
Come in.

04:00.980 --> 04:02.990
[Li Si]

04:15.080 --> 04:16.000
It's so windy.

04:16.560 --> 04:18.720
I'm afraid there will be
heavy rain tonight.

04:18.720 --> 04:19.269
Let's go.

04:19.750 --> 04:20.880
Let's go sit inside.

04:32.150 --> 04:33.330
[Lyu Yunsu]

04:38.120 --> 04:39.480
The rain in these mountains

04:39.480 --> 04:40.880
will easily make you sick

04:40.920 --> 04:41.920
if you get soaked.

04:42.310 --> 04:43.159
Sir, this young lady

04:43.159 --> 04:44.310
by your side

04:44.800 --> 04:46.190
doesn't look too well.

04:46.390 --> 04:48.050
Could she have caught a chill?

04:48.190 --> 04:49.590
Do you want something hot

04:49.630 --> 04:50.360
to warm up?

04:51.310 --> 04:51.970
No, thanks.

04:53.040 --> 04:54.310
We brought our own food.

04:54.310 --> 04:55.770
Thanks for your kindness.

04:55.950 --> 04:56.880
You're welcome.

04:59.280 --> 04:59.920
Thank you.

05:01.510 --> 05:02.510
Do you want some water?

05:02.510 --> 05:03.570
I don't want water.

05:03.800 --> 05:05.260
I'll throw up if I drink it.

05:05.480 --> 05:06.560
You're so weird.

05:07.070 --> 05:08.480
You don't throw up when you eat pancakes,

05:08.480 --> 05:10.610
but throw up just from drinking water.

05:20.600 --> 05:22.310
What exactly do you want to do here?

05:22.310 --> 05:24.040
I'm telling you, don't drag me into this.

05:24.040 --> 05:25.040
My sect has rules.

05:25.310 --> 05:28.120
We aren't allowed to
interfere in worldly affairs.

05:28.120 --> 05:29.600
There are so many people here.

05:29.600 --> 05:30.830
Even if you wanted to interfere,

05:30.830 --> 05:32.159
you probably couldn't.

05:46.950 --> 05:48.750
The wind is really strong today.

05:49.270 --> 05:51.159
Maybe no one will come tonight.

05:51.950 --> 05:53.010
That's hard to say.

05:53.600 --> 05:55.240
Recently, merchant traffic along this road

05:55.240 --> 05:56.700
has been unusually heavy—

05:57.000 --> 05:59.000
more than 10 times the usual amount.

05:59.390 --> 06:00.310
And this house

06:00.520 --> 06:01.750
is the only place within 20 miles

06:01.750 --> 06:03.530
where people can take shelter
from the rain.

06:03.530 --> 06:04.970
Didn't we all happen to

06:05.000 --> 06:06.460
come here by coincidence?

06:06.480 --> 06:08.270
This place is in Hanzhou.

06:08.560 --> 06:10.830
Bandits have been frequent
in recent years.

06:10.830 --> 06:13.030
It's sparsely populated and desolate.

06:13.240 --> 06:15.000
When I came here a few years ago,

06:15.160 --> 06:18.040
it was still in ruins.

06:18.190 --> 06:19.630
I didn't expect that recently,

06:19.630 --> 06:20.720
the trade here

06:20.830 --> 06:22.390
would become so busy—

06:22.750 --> 06:24.210
actually even more active

06:24.480 --> 06:26.040
and connected than before.

06:27.950 --> 06:29.080
As for the reason...

06:29.870 --> 06:31.310
Have you ever heard of

06:31.560 --> 06:34.420
the Gongshan Jade Tablet
and the Immortality Pill?

06:43.820 --> 06:45.230
Who doesn't know

06:45.390 --> 06:47.570
about such heavenly treasures?

06:47.830 --> 06:49.690
You should know that 50 years ago,

06:50.040 --> 06:51.750
the divine doctor Su Taiyi
of Chongling Valley

06:51.750 --> 06:52.680
announced to the public

06:52.680 --> 06:53.870
that he could refine an immortal elixir

06:53.870 --> 06:55.750
called the Immortality Pill

06:55.920 --> 06:58.040
that could make people live forever.

06:58.750 --> 07:01.210
Once the word got out,
the world was shocked.

07:01.240 --> 07:02.270
All the major immortal sects

07:02.270 --> 07:03.510
undoubtedly grabbed onto

07:03.510 --> 07:05.120
a lifeline.

07:05.390 --> 07:06.560
More than that.

07:07.070 --> 07:09.430
Immortality used to
be the privilege of gods

07:09.430 --> 07:10.510
and the ultimate goal

07:10.510 --> 07:11.770
for many cultivators.

07:12.160 --> 07:13.630
Now, no matter who it is,

07:13.870 --> 07:15.330
as long as they take a pill,

07:15.680 --> 07:16.810
they can achieve it.

07:17.430 --> 07:18.560
Do you think those high officials

07:18.560 --> 07:19.510
and nobles

07:19.830 --> 07:22.680
and the royal relatives of
secular dynasties don't want it?

07:22.680 --> 07:23.480
Thus,

07:23.800 --> 07:24.720
various forces

07:24.720 --> 07:26.720
exhausted all kinds of rare treasures

07:26.720 --> 07:27.720
and spared no effort

07:27.720 --> 07:29.750
to help Chongling Valley
refine the elixir.

07:29.750 --> 07:31.480
In order to thank everyone
for their kindness,

07:31.480 --> 07:33.040
Su Taiyi made 30 pieces of

07:33.040 --> 07:34.370
Gongshan Jade Tablets.

07:34.500 --> 07:35.890
They were distributed

07:35.920 --> 07:37.159
according to each faction's
level of contribution.

07:37.159 --> 07:38.920
It was said that
when it started to be forged,

07:38.920 --> 07:41.040
those holding a tablet could
exchange it for the medicine

07:41.040 --> 07:43.430
—and share immortality with the world.

07:43.720 --> 07:44.920
Share immortality?

07:45.430 --> 07:46.690
Easier said than done.

07:47.560 --> 07:48.510
Is this immortality

07:48.510 --> 07:51.120
something everyone can get?

07:52.240 --> 07:53.120
Sir, I wonder,

07:53.680 --> 07:56.190
if you also want immortality.

08:04.720 --> 08:06.040
I am an official,

08:06.650 --> 08:08.750
yet I can't even
afford a new pair of boots.

08:08.750 --> 08:10.070
How could a treasure like that

08:10.070 --> 08:11.510
ever fall to someone like me?

08:11.510 --> 08:12.720
That's a pity.

08:13.240 --> 08:14.630
Fifty years have passed,

08:14.630 --> 08:17.130
and the Immortality Pill
is about to be forged.

08:17.130 --> 08:18.160
Many disciples from immortal sects

08:18.160 --> 08:20.290
and officials from secular dynasties

08:20.390 --> 08:23.390
are passing through here
with the Gongshan Jade Tablet.

08:23.390 --> 08:24.950
If you are interested,

08:25.240 --> 08:27.040
you can wander around this road.

08:27.480 --> 08:29.160
Maybe you can pick one up.

08:29.720 --> 08:30.560
Pick one up?

08:31.240 --> 08:33.500
Such a treasure is worth more than a life.

08:33.600 --> 08:34.600
Who would lose it?

08:34.909 --> 08:36.240
Fifty years have passed,

08:36.240 --> 08:37.900
and things have changed a lot.

08:38.380 --> 08:40.080
Many prominent families
and immortal sects of the past

08:40.080 --> 08:41.030
have declined.

08:41.750 --> 08:43.120
The things in their hands

08:43.120 --> 08:45.250
naturally fell into the mortal world.

08:45.750 --> 08:47.120
For such unowned items,

08:47.440 --> 08:50.080
whoever picks them up owns them.

08:54.910 --> 08:55.970
My surname is Chen.

08:56.030 --> 08:56.890
I am a merchant.

08:57.550 --> 08:58.550
Sir, may I ask,

08:58.550 --> 09:00.320
since you are here
in your official uniform,

09:00.320 --> 09:01.920
are you here to handle a case?

09:03.080 --> 09:04.510
Indeed, I have a case to handle.

09:04.510 --> 09:05.910
But whether it can be done

09:06.600 --> 09:08.150
depends on whether everyone here

09:08.150 --> 09:09.550
is willing to cooperate.

09:19.320 --> 09:21.750
Sir, you must be joking.

09:22.790 --> 09:23.510
Is it funny?

09:24.390 --> 09:25.020
I am someone

09:25.020 --> 09:26.510
who is terrible at telling jokes.

09:26.510 --> 09:27.570
Is it really funny?

09:30.150 --> 09:31.790
I see you are dressed well,

09:32.270 --> 09:33.030
and your accompanying guards

09:33.030 --> 09:34.360
are all highly skilled.

09:34.480 --> 09:35.440
I wonder

09:35.600 --> 09:37.400
what kind of business you are in.

09:37.840 --> 09:39.440
Jiangnan is rich in silkworms
and fine silk.

09:39.440 --> 09:41.030
I'm simply taking advantage of the trend

09:41.030 --> 09:43.320
to make a living in the silk trade.

09:43.600 --> 09:44.750
in the silk trade.

09:45.480 --> 09:46.720
Silk business?

09:47.870 --> 09:49.510
Such delicate items

09:50.550 --> 09:51.880
are left out in the rain?

09:52.440 --> 09:53.750
When I just entered,

09:53.870 --> 09:55.320
I saw that the carriage outside

09:55.320 --> 09:57.200
was not even covered with cowhide.

09:57.200 --> 09:57.910
You are truly

09:57.910 --> 09:59.570
an "excellent" businessman.

10:05.080 --> 10:06.360
You look familiar.

10:07.000 --> 10:08.060
Where are you from?

10:09.750 --> 10:10.390
Lingnan.

10:11.030 --> 10:11.720
Lingnan?

10:13.370 --> 10:14.120
Recently in Lingnan,

10:14.120 --> 10:15.380
there was a major case.

10:15.790 --> 10:17.720
A group of escorts who lost their goods

10:17.720 --> 10:19.360
killed their employer's family.

10:19.360 --> 10:19.960
They even set a fire

10:19.960 --> 10:21.910
and burned down the employer's house.

10:21.910 --> 10:23.770
I wonder if you've heard about it.

10:25.510 --> 10:26.960
Lingnan is a huge place.

10:27.360 --> 10:28.720
We are ill-informed

10:29.120 --> 10:30.870
and haven't heard of it.

10:31.600 --> 10:32.270
Is that so?

10:34.080 --> 10:35.030
What a pity.

10:36.390 --> 10:37.390
A pity about what?

10:37.440 --> 10:38.410
It's a pity that before I left,

10:38.410 --> 10:40.000
I had already taken another bounty mission

10:40.000 --> 10:41.670
and had other
official business to attend to.

10:41.670 --> 10:42.870
Otherwise, I could've accompanied you all

10:42.870 --> 10:43.930
to Lingnan myself—

10:44.030 --> 10:45.910
to see whether,
on that scorched patch of earth,

10:45.910 --> 10:48.480
there are wronged spirits
crying for justice at night,

10:48.480 --> 10:51.280
or vengeful ghosts
coming to collect their debts.

10:59.150 --> 11:01.880
It seems this old gentleman
has something to say.

11:02.910 --> 11:04.480
I'm just an old man.

11:05.000 --> 11:06.130
I live by the weather

11:06.240 --> 11:07.640
and survive off the land.

11:08.080 --> 11:09.940
What could I possibly have to say?

11:11.200 --> 11:12.790
Don't sell yourself short.

11:13.390 --> 11:16.000
The names of Xiyu Sword
and Shuangfeng Scissors

11:16.000 --> 11:17.640
are known to everyone
in the martial arts world.

11:17.640 --> 11:18.840
I have taken the bounty on you two

11:18.840 --> 11:19.690
three times already,

11:19.690 --> 11:21.200
but never had the chance to meet you.

11:21.200 --> 11:22.270
Even in my dreams at night,

11:22.270 --> 11:23.670
I think about your heads.

11:26.510 --> 11:27.120
Everyone,

11:27.390 --> 11:28.630
this one's a tough target.

11:28.630 --> 11:29.690
Care to lend a hand?

11:30.440 --> 11:31.150
Fine.

11:32.110 --> 11:33.840
First, let's kill the hound of
the authorities,

11:33.840 --> 11:35.270
then we'll deal with the cargo owner.

11:35.270 --> 11:36.600
As for how to split the loot,

11:36.600 --> 11:37.720
we can discuss that

11:38.030 --> 11:39.430
after we finish them off.

11:53.520 --> 11:54.280
I told you

11:54.480 --> 11:56.440
that we can't interfere in
worldly affairs.

11:56.440 --> 11:57.970
Who asked you to interfere?

11:58.550 --> 11:59.610
You just sit tight.

12:00.120 --> 12:01.320
Once I deal with them,

12:02.080 --> 12:04.280
I'll cook noodles for you using his pot.

12:07.550 --> 12:09.000
Do you want to live or die?

12:11.320 --> 12:12.920
Are you also here to catch me?

12:14.020 --> 12:14.930
Don't you know

12:14.960 --> 12:16.200
what crime you committed?

12:16.200 --> 12:17.400
Falling into my hands

12:17.600 --> 12:18.480
is better than dying by their swords,

12:18.480 --> 12:19.200
right?

13:18.240 --> 13:18.790
Miss.

13:35.750 --> 13:37.360
I thought you were fragile,

13:37.670 --> 13:39.630
but I didn't expect you
to have such internal strength.

13:39.630 --> 13:40.550
Are you also here to snatch

13:40.550 --> 13:42.010
the Gongshan Jade Tablet?

13:42.630 --> 13:44.360
Although I have no intention
to fight with you,

13:44.360 --> 13:46.080
I cannot bear to see the weak suffer.

13:46.080 --> 13:47.670
This lady hasn't provoked you.

13:47.670 --> 13:48.870
You do your grabbing.

13:49.000 --> 13:49.750
Why hurt her?

13:50.880 --> 13:51.910
In some desolate mountain inn,

13:51.910 --> 13:53.200
where would a merciful Bodhisattva
like you come from?

13:53.200 --> 13:54.440
Let me use these scissors

13:54.440 --> 13:55.570
to cut open her belly

13:55.630 --> 13:56.240
and see

13:56.480 --> 13:57.720
if she has

13:57.910 --> 13:59.080
a black heart.

14:20.270 --> 14:21.550
Give them the jade tablet.

14:21.550 --> 14:22.880
I don't need to be cured.

14:23.200 --> 14:25.000
If I give it to them, you will die.

14:27.000 --> 14:28.600
Miss, you bravely intervened.

14:28.600 --> 14:29.860
I am willing to entrust

14:30.030 --> 14:31.480
the jade tablet I carry to you.

14:31.480 --> 14:32.210
I only beg you

14:32.850 --> 14:33.960
to take my young lady

14:33.960 --> 14:35.160
to Chongling Valley.

14:42.120 --> 14:43.270
Please,

14:43.790 --> 14:44.720
let him go.

14:46.120 --> 14:46.630
Miss.

14:46.750 --> 14:48.440
She is a pitiful girl.

14:48.910 --> 14:53.320
I feel a bit reluctant now.

14:54.080 --> 14:56.480
Since you don't dare to do it,

14:56.960 --> 14:58.620
why not give this opportunity

14:59.150 --> 15:00.550
to me?

15:01.790 --> 15:03.190
You don't look that good,

15:03.390 --> 15:04.750
but you have a beautiful dream.

15:04.750 --> 15:05.510
Sir,

15:05.780 --> 15:06.930
you just said

15:06.960 --> 15:08.870
you were not interested in
this Gongshan Jade Tablet.

15:08.870 --> 15:10.200
Why did you go back on your word?

15:10.200 --> 15:11.730
I am indeed not interested.

15:11.760 --> 15:12.360
But I have to take this man

15:12.360 --> 15:13.960
and the Gongshan Jade Tablet

15:14.240 --> 15:15.080
on him.

15:17.670 --> 15:18.550
Thief Li Si

15:18.750 --> 15:20.750
stole the Gongshan Jade Tablet
of Lord Ling's Mansion.

15:20.750 --> 15:22.410
The bounty is 20 taels of gold.

15:22.480 --> 15:23.840
Since I took this bounty,

15:23.840 --> 15:24.970
I must take you back.

15:25.440 --> 15:26.600
I cannot go with you.

15:29.240 --> 15:30.370
That's not up to you.

15:43.550 --> 15:44.670
Together. Go!

15:44.790 --> 15:46.000
Go! Hurry!

15:56.240 --> 15:56.870
Honey,

15:57.000 --> 15:57.530
let's go!

15:57.960 --> 15:58.420
Go!

15:58.440 --> 15:59.300
Can you escape?

16:08.000 --> 16:10.000
You two black-hearted old killers,

16:10.170 --> 16:10.930
since you

16:10.960 --> 16:11.870
met me today,

16:12.080 --> 16:13.480
how can I leave you alive?

16:14.790 --> 16:16.520
Are you the Lord of Rust-Sword?

16:17.200 --> 16:18.320
Exactly.

16:18.960 --> 16:20.000
When you get to the underworld,

16:20.000 --> 16:21.440
don't forget to tell the King of Hell

16:21.440 --> 16:23.480
that I gave you this fate.

16:44.550 --> 16:45.480
What do you want?

16:47.510 --> 16:48.710
I can go back with you.

16:50.120 --> 16:50.920
That's right.

16:51.670 --> 16:53.530
But not the Gongshan Jade Tablet.

16:53.790 --> 16:56.120
My young lady suffers from heart failure.

16:56.240 --> 16:57.640
Medicine cannot cure it.

16:57.840 --> 16:58.440
She needs

16:59.320 --> 17:01.600
the Immortality Pill to cure her illness.

17:01.600 --> 17:03.030
Everyone has their own difficulties.

17:03.030 --> 17:04.290
But I am a bounty guard,

17:04.349 --> 17:05.960
only responsible for catching thieves
and recovering stolen goods.

17:05.960 --> 17:07.619
You don't need to tell me this.

17:08.680 --> 17:09.410
My young lady

17:09.880 --> 17:10.740
is the daughter

17:12.000 --> 17:13.400
of General Lyu Jing.

17:26.150 --> 17:28.150
[Chongling Valley]

17:32.200 --> 17:33.660
Greetings, Grandmaster.

17:37.590 --> 17:38.350
Are you

17:39.000 --> 17:39.590
Zhu Yu?

17:40.430 --> 17:42.030
[Zhu Yu of Chongling Valley]

17:41.200 --> 17:42.270
Yes.

17:44.350 --> 17:45.350
You are so old now.

17:46.240 --> 17:47.510
I have no immortal perception

17:47.510 --> 17:48.770
and cannot cultivate.

17:48.920 --> 17:49.450
However,

17:49.960 --> 17:51.080
I haven't seen you

17:51.110 --> 17:52.350
for 50 years.

17:52.880 --> 17:54.590
I'm already 62 now.

17:54.960 --> 17:56.030
My physical body

17:56.270 --> 17:57.880
is maintained entirely by elixirs,

17:57.880 --> 17:59.340
so it looks quite "young".

18:02.680 --> 18:03.680
Where is Su Taiyi?

18:05.590 --> 18:08.120
The Immortality Pill
is about to be finished.

18:08.270 --> 18:10.670
Master is in seclusion refining the elixir

18:10.880 --> 18:11.830
on Mount Jiujue.

18:12.510 --> 18:14.440
In seclusion refining the elixir?

18:15.000 --> 18:15.830
Then why did he write

18:15.830 --> 18:16.690
to call me back?

18:17.480 --> 18:19.880
I wouldn't dare deceive you, Grandmaster.

18:20.350 --> 18:21.720
Actually, in recent years,

18:21.720 --> 18:23.520
Master has been looking for you.

18:23.830 --> 18:25.490
No matter where he heard news,

18:25.590 --> 18:27.200
as long as it sounded like you,

18:27.200 --> 18:28.730
Master would send a letter.

18:28.920 --> 18:30.310
This time, he heard

18:30.720 --> 18:33.720
that someone in the capital stood
against the immortal sect Heavenly Talent.

18:33.720 --> 18:35.240
Master wrote a letter as usual.

18:35.240 --> 18:37.880
He didn't hold much hope at first.

18:38.400 --> 18:39.460
But unexpectedly,

18:39.830 --> 18:40.920
it really is you.

18:50.350 --> 18:51.240
After you, Grandmaster.

18:50.650 --> 18:53.940
[Jiujue Cave]

19:08.880 --> 19:10.410
What is the meaning of this?

19:11.200 --> 19:13.110
The Immortality Pill
is about to be finished.

19:13.110 --> 19:14.570
Master needs to go all out.

19:14.960 --> 19:16.680
To prevent scoundrels from coveting it,

19:16.680 --> 19:18.270
Master specifically ordered me

19:18.270 --> 19:20.440
to completely seal this door.

19:22.440 --> 19:23.970
It's sealed quite tightly.

19:25.240 --> 19:26.000
Is it useful?

19:27.030 --> 19:27.720
It is.

19:28.510 --> 19:31.000
A dragon-severing stone
was also set up inside the cave.

19:31.000 --> 19:33.030
It can only be opened from the inside.

19:33.030 --> 19:33.640
If anyone

19:33.680 --> 19:35.200
tries to attack by force from the outside,

19:35.200 --> 19:37.400
this entire mountainside will collapse.

19:37.400 --> 19:39.510
By then, both the pill
and the people will be destroyed,

19:39.510 --> 19:40.910
leaving nothing behind.

19:42.640 --> 19:43.880
This Su Taiyi...

20:17.920 --> 20:18.720
What's wrong?

20:18.720 --> 20:19.850
Why are you sighing?

20:20.880 --> 20:22.440
I'm afraid I won't be able to solve

20:22.440 --> 20:23.440
this case of mine.

20:24.440 --> 20:25.110
Why?

20:28.000 --> 20:29.530
She's Lyu Jing's daughter.

20:32.150 --> 20:33.270
Who is Lyu Jing?

20:36.160 --> 20:37.030
He was a general

20:37.680 --> 20:39.240
who guarded the border of
Beixiang for many years.

20:39.240 --> 20:40.960
He was very brave and skilled in battle.

20:40.960 --> 20:41.830
The year before last,

20:41.830 --> 20:44.760
in the battle against
the barbarians at Laozhuang Station,

20:44.760 --> 20:45.790
he led 2,000 soldiers

20:45.790 --> 20:47.160
to defend the city for three months.

20:47.160 --> 20:49.680
They ran out of food
and ammunition, and died of exhaustion.

20:49.680 --> 20:50.510
I heard that the enemies thought

20:50.510 --> 20:51.570
he was a cultivator

20:51.790 --> 20:54.110
and wanted to
find his immortal perception.

20:54.110 --> 20:56.030
But after cutting open his corpse,

20:56.030 --> 20:57.350
they found that his stomach

20:57.350 --> 20:59.280
was full of grass roots, tree bark,

20:59.510 --> 21:01.110
and undigested incense ash.

21:02.110 --> 21:04.680
General Lyu Jing
guarded the border for years.

21:04.680 --> 21:05.960
His parents died early,

21:05.960 --> 21:07.360
and his wife passed away.

21:07.440 --> 21:09.240
I heard he only had one daughter,

21:09.640 --> 21:10.480
who is mute.

21:11.720 --> 21:13.250
I didn't expect it to be her.

21:20.000 --> 21:21.600
What illness did that guy say

21:21.640 --> 21:22.400
she has?

21:23.240 --> 21:24.400
Heart failure.

21:27.960 --> 21:29.560
Good people don't live long.

21:31.480 --> 21:34.110
Is Beixiang always at war?

21:38.790 --> 21:39.920
Do you know why I don't like

21:39.920 --> 21:40.920
you cultivators?

21:41.590 --> 21:42.310
Why?

21:43.000 --> 21:44.270
You seem to be like us,

21:45.160 --> 21:46.290
but also different.

21:46.750 --> 21:48.750
It's like you live in another world.

21:50.310 --> 21:51.880
We have our own rules too.

21:52.400 --> 21:54.130
Must rules always be followed?

21:54.510 --> 21:55.110
Of course.

21:55.480 --> 21:57.010
What if the rules are wrong?

21:57.720 --> 21:59.590
Every disciple
who enters the immortal sect

21:59.590 --> 22:00.850
must follow this rule.

22:01.270 --> 22:02.790
The immortal sects have been passed down
for thousands of years.

22:02.790 --> 22:03.790
If everyone could

22:03.790 --> 22:04.960
do whatever they want,

22:04.960 --> 22:07.350
the world would have been
in chaos long ago.

22:07.350 --> 22:08.200
So sometimes,

22:08.480 --> 22:10.790
even if you don't like it
or don't understand it,

22:10.790 --> 22:12.450
you have to comfort yourself,

22:12.510 --> 22:14.680
telling yourself the rules can't be wrong.

22:14.680 --> 22:15.750
Is that what they told you,

22:15.750 --> 22:17.410
or do you actually believe it?

22:19.760 --> 22:21.200
To our dynasty, General Lyu Jing

22:21.200 --> 22:22.830
was a hero who defended our country.

22:22.830 --> 22:24.350
But in the eyes of the enemy,

22:24.350 --> 22:26.420
he was a fierce and terrifying opponent.

22:26.420 --> 22:27.160
When the standpoint changes,

22:27.160 --> 22:28.560
the mind changes with it.

22:28.760 --> 22:29.350
In this world,

22:29.350 --> 22:31.350
nothing is absolutely infallible.

22:34.200 --> 22:35.600
Like the sword in my hand,

22:35.970 --> 22:37.080
it looks ordinary,

22:37.110 --> 22:38.680
but it is the greatest sword in the world.

22:38.680 --> 22:39.940
I firmly believe this.

22:40.310 --> 22:41.170
But do you think

22:41.680 --> 22:42.440
I am right?

22:51.160 --> 22:51.760
Forget it.

22:52.270 --> 22:53.110
After today,

22:53.160 --> 22:54.620
just pretend we never met.

23:07.750 --> 23:12.580
♪ Spending a lifetime,
I ask myself what I first sought ♪

23:13.770 --> 23:18.520
♪ What is it my heart truly desires ♪

23:16.750 --> 23:18.480
Must rules always be followed?

23:18.640 --> 23:19.750
What if the rules are wrong?

23:19.030 --> 23:22.020
♪ Step by step up the immortal stairway ♪

23:21.590 --> 23:23.000
To our dynasty, General Lyu Jing

23:22.440 --> 23:25.260
♪ I hear the shame of parting ♪

23:23.030 --> 23:24.640
was a hero defending our country.

23:24.640 --> 23:25.680
But to the enemy,

23:25.280 --> 23:27.840
♪ This immortal path admired by all ♪

23:26.240 --> 23:27.870
he was a fierce and terrifying opponent.

23:27.870 --> 23:30.750
♪ Can exist, or not exist ♪

23:28.310 --> 23:29.000
When standpoints change,

23:29.000 --> 23:30.260
mind change with them.

23:30.640 --> 23:31.270
In this world,

23:30.770 --> 23:33.430
♪ Once again I see
the world's cold indifference ♪

23:31.270 --> 23:33.450
there is nothing absolutely infallible.

23:33.450 --> 23:36.700
♪ Bending what I've cherished
all my life ♪

23:36.720 --> 23:42.070
♪ Illusions and vanity blind the eyes,
how could one still care ♪

23:42.700 --> 23:45.110
♪ Once again I see
the world's cold and heat ♪

23:45.280 --> 23:48.430
♪ If no one shares
its sorrow and suffering ♪

23:48.620 --> 23:54.220
♪ This path will only turn against
immortal laws and restraint ♪

24:06.270 --> 24:07.600
Why are you still awake?

24:11.750 --> 24:12.350
For me?

24:14.780 --> 24:15.380
Thank you.

24:17.640 --> 24:19.200
I throw up when I drink water,

24:19.200 --> 24:20.860
but eating flatbread is fine.

24:21.070 --> 24:22.930
Eating pears should be okay, too.

24:28.070 --> 24:30.070
Thank you for today.

24:31.240 --> 24:32.040
It's nothing.

24:34.240 --> 24:35.480
You are a cultivator.

24:38.720 --> 24:39.320
By the way,

24:39.480 --> 24:40.030
are you going

24:40.030 --> 24:41.200
to Chongling Valley next?

24:41.200 --> 24:42.160
I happen to be going there as well.

24:42.160 --> 24:43.490
We can travel together.

24:50.720 --> 24:51.030
I...

24:51.830 --> 24:53.510
I threw up when I drank water before.

24:53.510 --> 24:55.840
I didn't expect I couldn't even eat pears.

24:57.720 --> 24:59.050
I wasted your kindness.

25:00.520 --> 25:01.580
Get some rest soon.

25:01.920 --> 25:03.440
We have to hit the road tomorrow.

25:03.440 --> 25:04.070
I'm fine.

25:09.830 --> 25:10.960
What does this mean?

25:15.110 --> 25:16.440
Thank you.

25:18.160 --> 25:18.960
Get some rest.

25:40.640 --> 25:41.840
Let's part ways here.

25:42.510 --> 25:43.370
Part ways here.

25:45.000 --> 25:46.000
Next time we meet,

25:46.160 --> 25:48.020
don't fail to recognize me again.

25:50.030 --> 25:50.890
Part ways here.

26:01.270 --> 26:02.870
Why do you believe that sword

26:02.960 --> 26:04.620
is the best sword in the world?

26:06.680 --> 26:08.080
The sword seller told me.

26:08.590 --> 26:09.520
You believe him?

26:10.830 --> 26:11.960
I believe in myself.

26:13.590 --> 26:14.350
Farewell!

26:38.310 --> 26:39.200
Here.

26:39.220 --> 26:39.790
Stop.

26:40.440 --> 26:41.510
Stop.

26:43.740 --> 26:44.870
[Zhang Dahu]

26:44.350 --> 26:45.200
Over here.

26:46.400 --> 26:47.530
Let's go take a look.

26:48.750 --> 26:50.810
Are you heading to Chongling Valley?

26:51.550 --> 26:52.110
Yes.

26:53.070 --> 26:54.550
Finally, you're here.

26:54.790 --> 26:56.520
Are you from Chongling Valley?

26:56.800 --> 26:58.040
Yes, I am.

26:58.110 --> 26:59.720
Then you are here to...

27:00.030 --> 27:01.760
I came specially to pick you up.

27:03.350 --> 27:04.960
Let me briefly introduce it to you.

27:04.960 --> 27:06.270
The healers in Chongling Valley

27:06.270 --> 27:07.550
are mainly divided into 13 branches:

27:07.550 --> 27:09.550
major internal medicine,
minor internal medicine,

27:09.550 --> 27:11.590
wind disorders, obstetrics, ophthalmology,
reproductive disorders,

27:11.590 --> 27:13.400
miscellaneous medicine, dentistry,
throat medicine,

27:13.400 --> 27:15.920
bone-setting, acupuncture,
incantation therapy,

27:15.920 --> 27:17.200
and trauma and swelling treatment.

27:17.200 --> 27:18.030
What kind of illness

27:18.030 --> 27:19.230
are you here to treat?

27:24.750 --> 27:26.280
Can't hear, or can't speak?

27:26.480 --> 27:27.210
Can't speak.

27:27.550 --> 27:28.280
Can't speak.

27:29.000 --> 27:31.160
That would fall under throat medicine.

27:31.160 --> 27:33.720
Or possibly the ear
and eye obstruction branch.

27:33.720 --> 27:35.750
Miss, how long have you
had this condition?

27:35.750 --> 27:36.240
No.

27:36.920 --> 27:38.050
It's heart failure.

27:38.160 --> 27:39.030
Heart failure?

27:40.200 --> 27:42.200
Wait a minute. Heart failure...

27:45.200 --> 27:46.860
Heart disease and chest pain.

27:47.160 --> 27:48.590
You need to find Dr. Zhu for this.

27:48.590 --> 27:49.830
He's good at treating this.

27:49.830 --> 27:51.170
Doesn't she need the Immortality Pill?

27:51.170 --> 27:52.830
Why would you need an elixir for this?

27:52.830 --> 27:54.600
What kind of place
do you think Chongling Valley is?

27:54.600 --> 27:55.720
It's a sanctuary for patients,

27:55.720 --> 27:56.680
a palace for healers.

27:56.680 --> 27:57.260
Every single one of them

27:57.260 --> 27:58.910
is a master healer.

27:59.340 --> 28:00.230
No matter what illness,

28:00.230 --> 28:01.830
it will definitely be cured.

28:01.830 --> 28:03.640
So Chongling Valley

28:03.790 --> 28:05.720
can cure Miss Lyu's heart disease?

28:06.550 --> 28:07.600
Absolutely.

28:07.930 --> 28:08.790
Otherwise, why would you come

28:08.790 --> 28:09.720
all the way here?

28:09.880 --> 28:11.550
Put your mind at ease.

28:11.790 --> 28:13.510
It's definitely a worthwhile trip.

28:13.510 --> 28:14.110
Great.

28:15.110 --> 28:17.310
You must be exhausted from the journey.

28:17.590 --> 28:18.450
How about this?

28:18.830 --> 28:19.490
I'll drive,

28:19.750 --> 28:20.810
and you take a rest.

28:20.880 --> 28:22.140
We couldn't possibly.

28:22.440 --> 28:23.750
Don't mention it.

28:24.120 --> 28:24.830
Once you're in Chongling Valley,

28:24.830 --> 28:26.160
make yourselves at home.

28:26.160 --> 28:26.760
By the way,

28:26.830 --> 28:28.030
let me introduce myself.

28:28.030 --> 28:29.160
My surname is Zhang.

28:29.160 --> 28:29.820
Zhang Dahu.

28:30.110 --> 28:31.510
Just call me buddy Zhang.

28:32.240 --> 28:33.570
Thank you, buddy Zhang.

28:33.750 --> 28:34.510
No problem.

28:34.950 --> 28:35.480
Let's go.

28:39.550 --> 28:41.150
Is it okay to put the carriage

28:41.510 --> 28:42.400
here?

28:44.100 --> 28:45.100
Don't worry.

28:45.310 --> 28:46.830
Someone will look after it.

28:46.830 --> 28:48.290
That's quite thoughtful.

28:48.680 --> 28:49.310
Follow me.

28:57.160 --> 28:57.760
Everyone,

28:57.960 --> 28:58.960
please get on the boat.

28:58.960 --> 29:00.220
With such a small boat,

29:00.480 --> 29:01.940
and so many of us taking it,

29:02.070 --> 29:03.070
will it be unsafe?

29:03.200 --> 29:04.350
What if we fall into the water?

29:04.350 --> 29:06.000
Don't worry, I take the boat every day.

29:06.000 --> 29:06.590
Besides,

29:06.720 --> 29:08.200
my reputation as a great swimmer

29:08.200 --> 29:09.260
isn't for nothing.

29:09.560 --> 29:10.920
No matter who falls into the water,

29:10.920 --> 29:12.200
I can fish them out.

29:12.350 --> 29:12.880
Let's go.

29:21.640 --> 29:22.880
Miss, come.

29:25.240 --> 29:25.840
Slow down.

29:34.070 --> 29:34.920
Careful.

29:34.940 --> 29:35.670
Take it easy.

29:36.050 --> 29:37.130
Let's go!

29:37.160 --> 29:38.220
Miss, are you okay?

29:38.310 --> 29:38.910
Slow down.

29:39.030 --> 29:39.960
It's fine.

29:40.400 --> 29:41.530
We'll be there soon.

29:42.350 --> 29:43.280
Senior Brother,

29:43.570 --> 29:44.640
we agreed on this before.

29:44.640 --> 29:45.190
Okay, okay.

29:45.190 --> 29:45.880
I brought everyone.

29:45.880 --> 29:46.350
Let them in.

29:46.350 --> 29:46.720
Wait.

29:47.960 --> 29:49.620
How did their carriage get in?

29:53.400 --> 29:54.000
Look here.

29:54.070 --> 29:55.670
I already got the number tag.

29:55.720 --> 29:57.180
Come, please step inside.

30:01.590 --> 30:02.310
You two,

30:03.110 --> 30:04.440
let's have tea someday.

30:04.640 --> 30:05.070
Okay.

30:05.640 --> 30:06.920
Why aren't they lining up?

30:06.920 --> 30:07.310
You should

30:07.310 --> 30:08.680
respect the order of arrival.

30:08.680 --> 30:09.960
Exactly.

30:10.160 --> 30:11.490
Why can they cut in line?

30:11.510 --> 30:12.240
They

30:12.260 --> 30:13.440
already got a number tag at 3 AM.

30:13.440 --> 30:15.310
Anyone with a number tag
can enter directly.

30:15.310 --> 30:16.310
How can this be?

30:16.310 --> 30:17.640
Young Master, we are here.

30:17.640 --> 30:18.680
How could they get it in advance?

30:18.680 --> 30:19.550
When can we go in?

30:19.550 --> 30:20.200
Alas.

30:38.880 --> 30:40.640
We need to walk faster.

30:41.030 --> 30:41.880
If we make it in time,

30:41.880 --> 30:43.940
we can still have a meal at Cunsu Hall.

30:44.070 --> 30:44.880
Thank you for your trouble.

30:44.880 --> 30:45.400
Thanks.

30:45.830 --> 30:46.830
Don't mention it.

30:47.030 --> 30:48.550
This is what I do.

30:48.790 --> 30:49.320
Let's go.

30:57.480 --> 30:59.540
[Zhu Yu: 7th-rank apothecary,
expert in heart disease]

31:01.510 --> 31:02.510
With so many people here,

31:02.510 --> 31:03.970
how long do we have to wait?

31:05.070 --> 31:06.510
The medicine boy just said

31:06.510 --> 31:08.240
we'll get our turn before noon.

31:08.350 --> 31:09.550
Let's wait a bit more.

31:10.720 --> 31:12.850
It's all sorted. Come inside and wait.

31:19.310 --> 31:20.570
This is our number tag.

31:20.920 --> 31:21.650
Hold it well.

31:21.750 --> 31:22.680
We'll wait here.

31:22.690 --> 31:23.590
When we're called later,

31:23.590 --> 31:24.320
we just go in.

31:25.270 --> 31:26.800
Do we also need to wait here?

31:26.880 --> 31:27.400
Yes.

31:27.680 --> 31:28.940
It'll be our turn soon.

31:29.070 --> 31:30.200
After they call us,

31:30.310 --> 31:30.910
let Dr. Zhu

31:30.960 --> 31:32.290
examine her carefully.

31:32.960 --> 31:34.620
We are here to participate...

31:34.750 --> 31:36.640
What could be more important than life?

31:36.640 --> 31:37.790
Let's treat her illness first.

31:37.790 --> 31:38.590
That is true.

31:38.790 --> 31:39.240
But...

31:39.680 --> 31:40.680
No buts.

31:40.880 --> 31:41.590
You wait here.

31:41.590 --> 31:42.600
I'll go get you some water.

31:42.600 --> 31:43.260
Wait for me.

31:47.070 --> 31:49.310
What illness are you here
to see a doctor about?

31:49.310 --> 31:50.110
Lung abscess.

31:51.400 --> 31:52.440
Sorry to bother you.

31:52.440 --> 31:54.000
You know Grand Tutor Rong, right?

31:54.000 --> 31:55.550
I saw him being carried in,

31:55.680 --> 31:56.640
almost dying.

31:56.960 --> 31:57.830
And guess what happened?

31:57.830 --> 31:59.200
Dr. Zhu saved him.

31:59.510 --> 32:01.440
Dr. Zhu is really amazing.

32:01.590 --> 32:02.480
Absolutely.

32:02.720 --> 32:04.180
Dr. Zhu is the direct disciple

32:04.180 --> 32:05.550
of the miraculous physician Su.

32:05.550 --> 32:08.480
He has inherited all of Su's
true medical teachings.

32:08.680 --> 32:09.310
Everyone,

32:09.750 --> 32:11.240
you don't have to line up here.

32:11.240 --> 32:12.480
You can come over
when your number is called.

32:12.480 --> 32:13.280
It's the same.

32:13.310 --> 32:14.830
I will call everyone's number.

32:14.830 --> 32:16.350
I definitely won't leave anyone out.

32:16.350 --> 32:18.150
Tea is prepared in the side hall.

32:18.160 --> 32:19.750
You can go there to rest.

32:20.550 --> 32:21.280
Excuse me...

32:21.920 --> 32:22.680
Miss,

32:22.870 --> 32:24.100
[Chongling Valley – Huaiqing]

32:22.960 --> 32:24.350
how can I help you?

32:25.030 --> 32:26.020
We are here to participate in

32:26.020 --> 32:27.200
the Pill-Tasting Competition.

32:27.200 --> 32:28.830
Do we need to line up here too?

32:29.830 --> 32:30.630
Cultivators?

32:30.960 --> 32:31.480
Yes.

32:32.350 --> 32:33.240
Cultivators.

32:33.750 --> 32:35.550
Cultivators don't line up here.

32:37.350 --> 32:38.030
Next.

32:38.880 --> 32:40.480
Number Jiachen may go in now.

32:44.400 --> 32:44.880
Ma'am,

32:45.160 --> 32:46.440
you're number Jiachen;

32:46.440 --> 32:48.300
it's your turn for treatment now.

32:48.350 --> 32:48.970
Okay.

32:49.000 --> 32:49.480
Here.

32:49.640 --> 32:50.500
Let me help you.

32:50.550 --> 32:51.610
We have to hurry up.

32:51.750 --> 32:53.550
Something doesn't seem right.

32:59.070 --> 32:59.670
Excuse me,

33:00.830 --> 33:01.830
why did you leave?

33:02.650 --> 33:03.480
We are here to participate in

33:03.480 --> 33:04.400
the Pill-Tasting Competition.

33:04.400 --> 33:05.200
It's not here.

33:05.750 --> 33:07.000
Pill-Tasting...

33:09.400 --> 33:10.600
You are cultivators.

33:13.510 --> 33:15.110
Cultivators have to pay too.

33:15.240 --> 33:16.030
Pay for what?

33:16.230 --> 33:16.720
You...

33:16.960 --> 33:18.920
Taking the boat, guiding, getting numbers,

33:18.920 --> 33:20.740
seeing the doctor,
you have to pay for all of them.

33:20.740 --> 33:21.200
But

33:22.000 --> 33:23.440
we didn't see the doctor.

33:24.200 --> 33:25.200
You took the boat.

33:26.110 --> 33:27.570
Does everyone have to pay?

33:27.920 --> 33:29.720
Of course. What am I working for?

33:33.070 --> 33:33.800
Here you are.

33:34.350 --> 33:35.080
Is it enough?

33:35.720 --> 33:36.240
Enough.

33:40.720 --> 33:42.850
So cultivators can be reasonable too?

33:45.720 --> 33:46.680
Since you've paid,

33:46.680 --> 33:47.680
no taking it back.

33:47.790 --> 33:48.200
No.

33:48.800 --> 33:49.890
I want to ask where

33:49.920 --> 33:51.850
the Pill-Tasting Competition is.

33:52.550 --> 33:53.480
Longevity Hall.

33:53.510 --> 33:54.070
Turn right,

33:54.070 --> 33:55.070
and keep going up.

33:56.200 --> 33:57.110
Okay, thanks.

34:09.030 --> 34:09.630
Are you

34:09.760 --> 34:12.290
also here
for the Pill-Tasting Competition?

34:13.000 --> 34:14.929
My master is Xin Xiong. I am Xin Mei.

34:15.770 --> 34:17.870
[Wang Yanqing
of the Wang family of Jinqiu]

34:17.110 --> 34:18.710
Let's go up together then.

34:26.400 --> 34:27.800
What's the matter, Miss?

34:28.360 --> 34:29.230
May I ask, sir,

34:29.480 --> 34:30.880
did you also come by boat?

34:31.280 --> 34:31.880
What boat?

34:32.510 --> 34:34.030
The boat to cross the river.

34:34.030 --> 34:34.889
Why take a boat?

34:36.070 --> 34:38.600
How else do you cross the river
without a boat?

34:38.800 --> 34:39.800
There is a bridge.

34:40.190 --> 34:41.190
Is there a bridge?

34:43.800 --> 34:44.800
There is a bridge?

34:57.880 --> 34:58.400
Lu,

34:59.230 --> 35:00.690
when we came over just now,

35:00.770 --> 35:01.920
I saw many immortal sects

35:01.920 --> 35:02.820
coming to participate in the upcoming

35:02.820 --> 35:04.070
Pill-Tasting Competition.

35:04.070 --> 35:04.730
Do you think

35:04.950 --> 35:06.810
Immortal Xin might have come too?

35:12.440 --> 35:13.800
With her limited skills,

35:13.800 --> 35:15.130
she shouldn't be sent to

35:15.230 --> 35:17.490
participate in such an important event.

35:17.760 --> 35:19.290
With Su Taiyi's character,

35:19.890 --> 35:20.590
can he actually lock himself

35:20.590 --> 35:22.840
in the valley all the time
to refine pills?

35:22.840 --> 35:24.190
I just don't believe it.

35:27.280 --> 35:28.410
Where are you going?

35:47.220 --> 35:49.920
[In the desolate void]

35:50.090 --> 35:53.150
[Where can one seek immortality?]

35:53.480 --> 35:56.550
[Healing the World]

35:57.180 --> 35:58.980
[Mr. Baiyun of Lingxu Sect]

36:00.120 --> 36:02.210
[Cai En of Zigai Mountain]

36:05.540 --> 36:07.820
[Zhi Bocheng,
Transit Commissioner of Jingzhou]

36:11.910 --> 36:14.300
[Master Fu of Qingshan Sect]

36:14.370 --> 36:16.370
[Longevity Hall]

36:34.670 --> 36:36.320
Where are the people from Tianyuan Sect's
Solar and Lunar Cavern

36:36.320 --> 36:37.550
and Xiaoyao Sect?

36:37.920 --> 36:39.030
Master Gongyu from
the Solar and Lunar Cavern

36:39.030 --> 36:40.510
is on his way.

36:41.230 --> 36:43.290
He will activate the formation later

36:43.920 --> 36:45.450
and project his image here.

36:47.360 --> 36:49.110
Xiaoyao Sect is in Beixiang.

36:49.230 --> 36:50.360
It's a long journey,

36:50.760 --> 36:52.620
so they should be on their way too.

36:52.920 --> 36:54.880
Did Tianyuan Sect inform anyone

36:55.510 --> 36:56.770
when they will arrive?

36:57.670 --> 36:59.070
Why are you looking at me?

36:59.400 --> 37:00.230
How would I know

37:00.230 --> 37:01.800
that Tianyuan Sect isn't coming?

37:01.800 --> 37:02.840
I think

37:03.030 --> 37:05.110
they encountered some accident on the way

37:05.110 --> 37:06.360
and can't make it.

37:08.150 --> 37:09.680
Why isn't Su Taiyi here yet?

37:10.110 --> 37:11.190
My master is at Mount Jiujue,

37:11.190 --> 37:12.480
cultivating in seclusion to refine pills.

37:12.480 --> 37:13.840
It has reached the final stage.

37:13.840 --> 37:15.670
It is crucial and allows no mistakes,

37:15.670 --> 37:17.330
so he couldn't come in person.

37:17.400 --> 37:20.060
How many pills
will this first furnace produce?

37:20.360 --> 37:21.090
I'm not sure.

37:22.000 --> 37:23.110
Then when will the Divine Doctor Su

37:23.110 --> 37:24.370
come out of seclusion?

37:26.070 --> 37:26.800
I don't know.

37:28.030 --> 37:29.670
You don't know this or that.

37:30.070 --> 37:31.800
Then why did you summon us here?

37:32.470 --> 37:34.070
I gathered you all here today

37:34.200 --> 37:35.160
mainly to count

37:35.190 --> 37:37.390
the Gongshan Jade Tablets in your hands

37:37.600 --> 37:40.030
and to distribute
the Immortality Pills next.

37:40.030 --> 37:42.360
Senior Brother Zhu Yu
is in charge of this.

37:45.280 --> 37:46.230
Zhu Yu?

37:47.030 --> 37:47.690
Where is he?

37:48.600 --> 37:49.360
Senior Brother Zhuyu

37:49.360 --> 37:51.030
is still seeing patients at Suwen Hall

37:51.030 --> 37:52.430
and will be here shortly.

38:18.620 --> 38:20.940
[Su Taiyi of Chongling Valley]

38:24.960 --> 38:25.510
Come.

38:26.630 --> 38:27.230
Master,

38:27.440 --> 38:28.640
everything is ready.

38:28.670 --> 38:29.360
Good.

38:32.800 --> 38:34.670
The Immortality Pill is not refined yet.

38:34.670 --> 38:35.800
You are early, sir.

38:49.760 --> 38:51.670
Master, Uncle Chu Ying,

38:51.920 --> 38:53.400
you scared me to death.

38:53.840 --> 38:55.500
I thought you were assassins.

38:56.920 --> 38:58.850
Aren't you always extremely bold?

38:58.880 --> 39:00.810
Are you still afraid of assassins?

39:02.230 --> 39:03.480
I'm getting older.

39:06.000 --> 39:07.150
Master, Uncle Chu Ying,

39:07.150 --> 39:08.230
please come in.

39:30.070 --> 39:30.630
My Lady.

39:31.710 --> 39:32.280
My Lady.

39:32.550 --> 39:33.880
Have you stared enough?

39:35.480 --> 39:36.880
I'm sorry, Master Gongyu.

39:36.880 --> 39:38.540
My friend is not a cultivator.

39:38.550 --> 39:40.180
He doesn't know the rules here.

39:40.180 --> 39:41.140
Then tell him

39:41.630 --> 39:42.560
what he should do

39:43.480 --> 39:44.880
and what he shouldn't do.

39:56.960 --> 39:57.630
Who is he?

39:59.330 --> 40:01.480
Master Gongyu
of the Solar and Lunar Cavern.

40:01.480 --> 40:02.540
He has a bad temper.

40:05.890 --> 40:07.960
Everyone is here to use
the Gongshan Jade Tablet

40:07.960 --> 40:10.090
to exchange for the Immortality Pill?

40:11.860 --> 40:13.040
Were their Gongshan Jade Tablets

40:13.040 --> 40:14.840
also given by Chongling Valley?

40:15.360 --> 40:16.230
Not exactly.

40:16.840 --> 40:18.510
Back then,
the Twelve Immortal Sects fully supported

40:18.510 --> 40:20.280
Divine Physician Su
in establishing Chongling Valley,

40:20.280 --> 40:22.440
saving lives
and refining the Immortality Pill.

40:22.440 --> 40:24.280
Later, based on each sect's contribution,

40:24.280 --> 40:25.800
a total of 30

40:25.800 --> 40:26.960
Gongshan Jade Tablets were distributed,

40:26.960 --> 40:29.590
to be used for exchange
when the pills were ready.

40:29.590 --> 40:31.050
With the rise of new forces

40:31.110 --> 40:32.640
and the decline of old ones,

40:32.860 --> 40:34.100
many Gongshan Jade Tablets

40:34.100 --> 40:35.830
have changed hands many times.

40:36.790 --> 40:37.520
So,

40:38.070 --> 40:39.000
you have one too?

40:39.440 --> 40:39.960
Yes.

40:40.370 --> 40:41.360
Then which of the Twelve Immortal Sects

40:41.360 --> 40:42.090
are you from?

40:42.800 --> 40:43.100
I...

40:43.120 --> 40:44.150
You came with her,

40:44.800 --> 40:46.860
but don't know which sect she's from?

40:48.440 --> 40:49.800
She's from the famous Xin Xie Manor

40:49.800 --> 40:51.960
among the Twelve Immortal Sects.

41:03.360 --> 41:04.490
Master, be careful.

41:12.130 --> 41:13.510
Master, come, let me do it.

41:13.510 --> 41:15.550
Your place is called Jiujue Cave?

41:20.320 --> 41:20.960
Master.

41:21.960 --> 41:22.510
Master.

41:22.550 --> 41:24.840
Don't you have a powerful

41:25.030 --> 41:25.900
and bloodthirsty

41:25.900 --> 41:27.760
divine weapon, the Jiujue Sword?

41:27.960 --> 41:29.480
I just borrowed its name

41:29.670 --> 41:31.590
to call this place Jiujue Cave.

41:32.430 --> 41:33.230
Sound mighty?

41:36.030 --> 41:37.490
You are living a good life.

41:38.920 --> 41:40.650
Where is the Immortality Pill?

41:40.670 --> 41:41.190
There,

41:41.630 --> 41:42.360
it's burning.
